{"tid":2203604,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"21年浪蕩人生 - Sid Vicious","createTime":"2020-09-15T12:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:36:48.000Z","uid":40662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f4e5bd06dc22c2752712cbd02ea56b3db6f381c","tid":2203604,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:39:20.000Z","msg":"[quote]<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/rbiyx2cc.0wtoupm14wc.wmgp5az2w3r.kvq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Frbiyx2cc.0wtoupm14wc.wmgp5az2w3r.kvq.jpg&h=ab3e1283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJohn Simon Ritchie (Sid Vicious原名) 出生於倫敦東南區Lewisham一個問題家庭，佢老母係道友，老豆係白金漢宮嘅衛兵，同時亦都係倫敦某間爵士俱樂部嘅半職業伸縮喇叭手，佢喺個仔出世冇耐就冇咗影。1965年，Ritchie個老母再婚，但唔夠半年個新老公就生Cancer死咗！極度複雜嘅家庭背景，令本性內向又缺乏母愛嘅Ritchie變得越來越暴戾，慢慢仲遺傳埋老母鋪毒癮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/chpyzedp.pbst2l2doaf.vqyx1ays5lv.pwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fchpyzedp.pbst2l2doaf.vqyx1ays5lv.pwv.jpg&h=24286515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRitchie本身係Sex Pistols嘅Die-hard fans，同Johnny Rotten喺學生時代已經Friend過打Band，喺成為隊中成員之前佢曾經幫Siouxsie and the Banshees以及由The Clash結他手Keith Levene組成嘅樂團The Flowers of Romance做過客串鼓手，其餘時間就多數都係匿喺Malcolm McLaren同Vivienne Westwood位於King's Road一間名叫Let It Rock嘅精品店度打躉。1977年，Ritchie應Malcolm McLaren、Johnny Rotten邀請加入Sex Pistols，以取代Bass手Glen Matlock嘅位置，並正式起名為Sid Vicious (藝名係取材自Rotten屋企隻惡死倉鼠)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/k0u25qsu.hz5xo24w5fb.aeb2nkzjnpq.jh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fk0u25qsu.hz5xo24w5fb.aeb2nkzjnpq.jh2.jpg&h=d04ecc88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾所周知，Sid Vicious根本就唔係乜嘢曠世音樂奇才，手Bass更加係完全唔掂，甚至有傳樂團每次出Show都會搵人企喺後台幫佢代彈。既然外界將Sid形容到咁鬼不堪，何解又會有成千上萬嘅歌迷為佢而瘋狂呢？原因係鍾意聽Punk Rock嘅族群一般都唔會拘泥於Performer嘅音準同演奏技巧，反而會比較側重於思想解放，而一向衣著出位、行風怪異嘅Sid Vicious正正就係佢哋所追求嘅逆主流文化代言人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/wzallzqz.gzzeptkjehe.qtahpxqdfil.ini.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fwzallzqz.gzzeptkjehe.qtahpxqdfil.ini.jpg&h=3ba673e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有關Sid嘅&ldquo;經典行徑&rdquo;實在太多！用單車鏈攻擊記者；串班男觀眾係Gay佬；掟酒樽落台導致一名女fans受重傷；爆晒缸都要搽啲血落心口繼續忘我演出；同著名MV導演Julien Temple鳩吹話自己係&ldquo;Pogo Dance&rdquo;發明人，藉此串盡一眾偽Punk迷；將Frank Sinatra首代表作My Way摧殘到體無完膚，走音甩Beat唔在講，喺MV結尾仲要掹槍大玩隨機射殺，成個感覺就似係兜口兜面對住班身光頸靚嘅上流貴族猛吐口水一樣，荒誕程度直達滿分，有唔少樂迷都認為呢段表演係Sid入團以來嘅最大貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n完整全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2020/09/CoCoAndMe-September-TemptressMoon.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F09%2FCoCoAndMe-September-TemptressMoon.html&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=fefadcca\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2020/09/CoCoAndMe-September-TemptressMoon.html</a>"},{"pid":"6582af10b068b0568cf6f9f1d394496db4990304","tid":2203604,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/kyzkl5zi.5kesg51tepz.3bz0hrkz4q5.sm5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fkyzkl5zi.5kesg51tepz.3bz0hrkz4q5.sm5.jpg&h=59405ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/mvaltmdi.vqxtvbkacr0.tnfgswevscy.qfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fmvaltmdi.vqxtvbkacr0.tnfgswevscy.qfk.jpg&h=5193ee88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/vsuyxk41.rucwo2btrq4.dqzj1rfvzqh.ojt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fvsuyxk41.rucwo2btrq4.dqzj1rfvzqh.ojt.jpg&h=e2d2b1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/0tzf104d.5g40vneduci.dbcj